。海關回覆查詢時指，根據《商品說明條例》，任何人將任何應用偽造商標的貨品，或將任何以虛假方式應用某商標，或與某一商標極為相似而相當可能會使人受欺騙的標記的貨品出售或展示，即屬違法。</blockquote><br />\n李生你返去問下你D同胞點解會咁"},{"pid":"a944b78266428aa973f3fad7133f6e6cb128199f","tid":731411,"uid":96,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:14:43.000Z","msg":"貢茶已經夠難飲 居然仲有人抄貢茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dd8df4026474cf38d705a6f2acda4716ddc62e","tid":731411,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:15:50.000Z","msg":"狗屎抄垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261a28b2e547097499fd4828a83746c340f1669c","tid":731411,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1fb0816b24ce912437c013c1667e133224803cc","tid":731411,"uid":145550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c9648de5268daac99d7553d8607043bd67b2ab70","tid":731411,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:08:23.000Z","msg":"幾時有假大家樂 大快活<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"間嘢係咪叫大快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"大家食J"},{"pid":"bea7378b35b1de26fc165a0e9d76671dd2cab87c","tid":731411,"uid":191762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T07:17:24.000Z","msg":"未見識過假波衫？"}]}